https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NSYNCnew-single-Better-Place-announcement-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NSYNCnew-single-Better-Place-announcement-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NSYNCnew-single-Better-Place-announcement-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NSYNCnew-single-Better-Place-announcement-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/NSYNCnew-single-Better-Place-announcement-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/n-sync">*NSYNC</a>宣布了 20 多年来的第一首新歌“Better Place”。</p><p>这个由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/justin-timberlake">贾斯汀·汀布莱克 (Justin Timberlake</a> )、克里斯·柯克帕特里克 (Chris Kirkpatrick)、JC Chasez、乔伊·法通 (Joey Fatone) 和兰斯·巴斯 (Lance Bass) 组成的男孩乐队于周二（9 月 12 日）在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/here-are-all-the-winners-from-the-2023-mtv-vmas-3496804">2023 年 MTV VMA</a>上重聚<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nsync-reportedly-set-to-reunite-at-2023-vmas-3496818">，并为泰勒·斯威夫特颁奖</a>。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/justin-timerlake-man-woods-review-2230941">贾斯汀·汀布莱克——《林中人》评论</a></strong></li></ul><p>在此之前， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nsync-appear-to-be-teasing-reunion-single-for-new-trolls-movie-3492732">该乐队的回归歌曲在</a>第三部<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/trolls-film-review-1652915"><em>《魔发精灵》</em></a>电影<em>《魔发精灵乐队》</em>的海报上被调侃。宣传片以 *NSYNC 标志为特色，并通过二维码引导粉丝访问包含音乐片段的<a href="https://www.takeyoutoabetterplace.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">网站</a>。</p><p>现在，同一网页已确认“Better Place”将于 9 月 29 日星期五发行。您可以<a href="https://www.tiktok.com/music/Better-Place-From-TROLLS-Band-Together-7277971663038679042" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>收听即将发行的单曲的片段。</p><p>这首歌也在<em>Trolls Band Together</em>的官方预告片中进行了预览 - 请在下面查看。</p><p> *NSYNC 最近在社交媒体上通过对<em>《老友记》</em>中乔伊和瑞秋讨论团队内部秘密的经典场景进行口型同步来暗示这一消息。 </p><p><iframe title="巨魔乐队齐聚 |官方预告片" w